<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 04:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:31:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-92cc-d7a8-afcf-baef8e050000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡让以色列为民主而战。现在他正在让它为自己的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</link><description>总理的助手们已经在为内塔尼亚胡战后的政治生存收集弹药，但公众不太可能让他保住自己的席位。他的继任者将不得不面对内塔尼亚胡留下的灾难性遗产</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 01:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-made-israel-fight-for-its-democracy-now-hes-making-it-fight-for-its-life/0000018b-92b5-db7e-af9b-fbf797670000</guid></item><item><title>以色列尚未从内塔尼亚胡时代的学说中清醒过来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 00:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-hasnt-sobered-up-yet-from-its-netanyahu-era-doctrine/0000018b-919e-d477-a1ff-f79ece710000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将税收收入转移给巴勒斯坦权力机构，但扣除流向加沙的资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</link><description>内阁还决定，以色列将不再允许加沙工人进入该国，并将10月7日在以色列的加沙人送回加沙地带</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:47:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-transfer-tax-revenue-to-palestinian-authority-but-deducts-gaza-bound-funds/0000018b-9255-db7e-af9b-fbd7201a0000</guid></item><item><title>“耶路撒冷的孩子们问我：圣诞老人，尽管有战争，你还会来吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：即使在战争中，以色列唯一经过认证的圣诞老人仍为欢乐而战，度蜜月的新婚夫妇则与家乡的损失作斗争</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 23:34:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-03/ty-article/.highlight/children-in-jerusalem-ask-me-santa-will-you-come-despite-the-war/0000018b-9247-db71-a7df-ffcfb7f20000</guid></item><item><title>他记录了田园诗般的基布兹的最后几年。他死于哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</link><description>就在几个月前，Kfar Azza 的居民动员起来帮助 Yahav Winner 将基布兹变成了他的第一部故事片的拍摄地。拍摄电影和第一个孩子的出生是他一生中最幸福的日子。 10 月 7 日，他在保护家人的过程中被谋杀。他还留下了被毁社区的最后大量文件</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:47:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-captured-his-kibbutzs-final-years-he-died-in-the-hamas-massacre-that-decimated-it/0000018b-9140-db7e-af9b-fbc306ed0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对抗内塔尼亚胡的秘密武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</link><description>拜登总统没有责骂内塔尼亚胡，而是制定了“紧紧拥抱比比”的策略。最近的书籍揭示了两人在 2021 年加沙一轮战斗中进行的长时间会谈的内容，以及总统断言以色列停止的时候到了</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:40:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/bidens-secret-weapon-vis-a-vis-netanyahu/0000018b-91e7-db7e-af9b-fbe75acf0000</guid></item><item><title>西岸好战分子斯莫特里奇必须被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:32:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-03/ty-article-opinion/west-bank-warmonger-smotrich-must-be-fired/0000018b-919e-db71-a7df-fddfcc7e0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯前往以色列推动加沙战斗的“人道主义暂停”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-to-push-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-9201-db7e-af9b-fbc392870000</link><description>美国国务卿还预计向以色列领导人施压，要求他们了解战后加沙的愿景</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 22:03:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-03/ty-article/.premium/blinken-heads-to-israel-to-push-for-humanitarian-pauses-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-9201-db7e-af9b-fbc392870000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役军人在约旦河西岸被杀，定居者焚烧汽车以示报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-west-bank-settlers-torch-cars-in-revenge/0000018b-9116-d477-a1ff-f7162d900000</link><description>巴勒斯坦卫生部报告称，周四，在盖勒吉利耶和比雷赫发生的其他事件中，包括一名 14 岁男孩在内的 3 名巴勒斯坦人被以色列国防军杀害</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 21:39:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-reservist-killed-in-west-bank-settlers-torch-cars-in-revenge/0000018b-9116-d477-a1ff-f7162d900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内政部长不顾财政部长反对向阿拉伯城镇提供资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</link><description>8 月，极右翼宗教犹太复国主义党的财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇 (Bezalel Smotrich) 发誓要暂停提供资金，直到能够证实这笔钱不会落入阿拉伯犯罪分子手中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:57:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israels-interior-minister-sends-funds-to-arab-towns-over-finance-ministers-objection/0000018b-9117-d7a8-afcf-bbb749840000</guid></item><item><title>内塔亚胡既虚弱又害怕。他必须走</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 19:55:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-02/ty-article-opinion/.premium/nentayahu-is-weak-and-afraid-he-must-go/0000018b-9163-d477-a1ff-f763c5a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席表示，如果医院燃料耗尽，以色列将允许进入加沙；内塔尼亚胡称他不同意</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</link><description>赫兹尔·哈勒维否认加沙医院燃料短缺的报道，承诺未来进入加沙地带的燃料将受到监控，以免到达哈马斯</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:44:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-israel-to-allow-fuel-into-gaza-for-hospitals-netanyahu-disputes-this/0000018b-9111-d7a8-afcf-bbb377200000</guid></item><item><title>“系统性的政治迫害”：加沙战争中对以色列-阿拉伯人的迫害是什么样子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</link><description>逮捕、审讯、解雇、大学开除——在最近一波可能撕裂以色列社会脆弱结构的事件中，阿拉伯公民成为以色列安全官员甚至他们自己同事的目标</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/systematic-witch-hunt-what-persecution-of-israeli-arabs-looks-like-amid-gaza-war/0000018b-90db-db7e-af9b-fbdb254e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列参加意大利漫画节引发加沙战争愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</link><description>以色列兄弟阿萨夫·哈努卡 (Asaf Hanuka) 和托梅尔·哈努卡 (Tomer Hanuka) 本应在今年的卢卡漫画和游戏节上受到招待，但以色列大使馆的参与导致几位艺术家退出。最终，兄弟俩决定不参加：“我们不想从真正的战争转向媒体战争”</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/israeli-presence-at-italian-comics-festival-draws-ire-over-gaza-war/0000018b-90e4-d7a8-afcf-bae7b9b60000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的“后天”困境将为真主党的下一步行动铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</link><description>德黑兰正在协助哈马斯、维持其在该地区的其他立足点并避免与美国直接军事对抗</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 17:24:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/irans-day-after-dilemma-will-pave-hezbollahs-next-steps/0000018b-8cce-db71-a7df-fdcf78b80000</guid></item><item><title>“我们知道你住在哪里”：自以色列与哈马斯战争以来，瑞典犹太人感到不安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-hamas-war-has-shaken-swedish-jews-sense-of-security/0000018b-9081-d7a8-afcf-baa356450000</link><description>学生们呆在家里不上课或上课并遭受虐待，抗议者呼吁消灭以色列，激进的伊斯兰组织不受约束地活动。在加沙战争和大规模屠杀的背景下，瑞典犹太社区担心其安全</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 17:23:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-02/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israel-hamas-war-has-shaken-swedish-jews-sense-of-security/0000018b-9081-d7a8-afcf-baa356450000</guid></item><item><title>在世界各地，针对犹太人的威胁的新时代已经开始</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/around-the-world-a-new-era-of-threats-against-jews-has-begun/0000018b-90af-db71-a7df-fdef9f580000</link><description>我错误地认为从英国到美国的犹太人不再面临重大威胁。正如过去几周所表明的那样，反犹太主义依然存在，对散居海外的犹太人构成了真正的死灰复燃的威胁</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:40:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/around-the-world-a-new-era-of-threats-against-jews-has-begun/0000018b-90af-db71-a7df-fdef9f580000</guid></item><item><title>继哈马斯之后，国际干预是加沙唯一选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/this-international-intervention-in-gaza-could-be-the-first-step-toward-a-palestinian-state/0000018b-8f49-d7a8-afcf-afeb97640000</link><description>随着巴勒斯坦人向建国过渡，国际维和人员驻扎在加沙地带和约旦河西岸的概念并不新鲜，但长期以来被忽视。美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯刚刚暗示，这可能是哈马斯事件后第二天的一个选择</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:39:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/this-international-intervention-in-gaza-could-be-the-first-step-toward-a-palestinian-state/0000018b-8f49-d7a8-afcf-afeb97640000</guid></item><item><title>从也门向以色列发射导弹：史无前例的发射、史无前例的拦截</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</link><description>伊朗本周从也门发射到埃拉特的导弹——距离至少 1,600 公里——打破了两项记录：从地面炮台发射弹道导弹的最远射程，以及以色列“箭”导弹防御系统首次对弹道导弹进行实战拦截系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 02 Nov 2023 16:34:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-02/ty-article/.premium/missile-from-yemen-to-israel-unprecedented-launch-unprecedented-interception/0000018b-8f88-d7a8-afcf-afab9c5e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>